    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The primary validation evidence demonstrates CFD-predicted RH index within ±15% of experimental measurements across all five COU operating points, with correct identification of the worst-case condition. Six factors were not assessed per MRL 2 scoping, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
